    {
      "id": "dacn-datn-propose_chunk_2",
      "text": "[Section: dacn-datn-propose > Các đề tài đề xuất > Đề tài 1: Multimodal Communication Assistant for the Hearing-Impaired]\n\n**Description:**\n+ Hearing-impaired talking to Normal-hearing: Real-time camera stream -> Interprets sign language -> Converts into corresponding text -> Use Text-To-Speech model to generate Spoken language\n+ Normal-Hearing talking to Hearing-Impaired: Spoken language -> ASR model to generate text -> text-to-sign generation -> visual display (show gestures and optionally support text)",
      "source": "/Users/frankie/Library/CloudStorage/onedrive/BK227/CO4029-Specialized-Project/capstone-project/Phase_2/backend/test_parsing/output/docx/dacn-datn-propose.json",
